Prerequisits:
Minecraft Forge Build 171
http://jenkins.minecraftforge.net:7070/job/forge/171

Minecraft Coder Pack 6.2
http://mcp.ocean-labs.de/index.php/MCP_Old_Releases
https://www.dropbox.com/sh/7msi3be7pd9uxpm/ySgvkS60df/mcp62.zip

Minecraft 1.2.5
http://www.minecraftmine.org/minecraft-1-2-5-jar/

Setup:
Download Minecraft 1.2.5 jar.
Download official Minecraft launcher.
Run Minecraft once to download .minecraft directory

Download Minecraft Coder Pack 6.2 and extract somewhere
Download Minecraft Forge 171 and extract forge directory into mcp base directory

copy bin/ and resources/ directories from .minecraft directory into jars/ directory in mcp base dir

Run forge install script.

clone Bookcase project into src/minecraft/net/minecraft/src
